{"id": "chunk_300_500", "start_word": 300, "end_word": 499, "text": "more information on our services, you’ll find everything you need to know right here. For help, contact us here How Triple Pay works You pick a sum assured you want to earn in the future and start saving periodically towards it. Then Heirs Life pays you three bulk payments within the saving tenure in this order: 1. 25% of the sum assured is paid at one-third of the savings period 2. Another 25% of the sum assured is paid at two-third of the savings period 3. An additional 100% of the sum assured plus bonus is paid at the end of the duration For peace of mind, if the unfortunate happens to you while saving, your beneficiary still earns the complete 100% of the sum assured plus bonus Document Requirements Duly Filled Proposal Form. Evidence of Payment. Valid means of ID - Driver license, Voter's card, NIMC, National ID, International Passport. Proof of residence - Utility Bill, Front page of the customer's address (same address as indicated on the form or portal), Local government levy. Duly Filled CTR, Financial Questionnaire, Address Verification Form, Bank Statement not more than 6-months (if premium is more than N5 million). We’re human, above all", "source": "html_files\\all-insurance-products\\personal-fam\\triple-pay-investment\\index.html", "chunk_index": 2, "title": "Triple Pay Investment - Heirs Insurance Group", "headings": ["Triple Pay Investment", "Already insured?Heirs takes care of everything.", "Perfect for anyone", "SHARE :", "Triple Pay Investment", "FAQs", "We’re human, above all else", "Company", "Quick Links", "Get Insurance", "Legal", "Download our App"], "links": [{"text": "", "href": "../../../index.html@p=4925.html"}, {"text": "About Us", "href": "index.html#"}, {"text": "Heirs Life", "href": "../../../heirs-life/index.html"}, {"text": "Heirs General", "href": "../../../heirs-general/index.html"}, {"text": "Heirs Insurance Brokers", "href": "https://heirsinsurancebrokers.com/